Report a parse error if there is a throw followed by a semicolon or newline.  The grammar has a "[no LineTerminator here]" so "throw;" or "throw \n expr;" are illegal.  https://people.mozilla.org/~jorendorff/es6-draft.html#sec-throw-statement  Fixes #652 ------------- Created by MOE: http://code.google.com/p/moe-java MOE_MIGRATED_REVID=77109093
